[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0696","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0696.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0458","title":"L0phtcrack 临时文件密码信息泄露漏洞","description":"L0phtcrack 2.5 在 Windows 系统临时目录（TEMP）中存储临时文件，这些文件可能包含明文密码信息。本地攻击者若能够访问目标系统的临时目录，可读取这些未清理的临时文件，从而窃取用户的密码凭据。该漏洞影响 L0phtcrack 2.5 版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，攻击前提是攻击者已获得本地文件系统访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0458"],"sources":["avd","cve"],"published":"1999-01-06","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 L0phtcrack 至不受影响的版本，新版已在内存中处理密码哈希而非写入临时文件。同时应确保系统 TEMP 目录配置正确的 NTFS 权限（仅允许当前用户访问），并定期清理临时目录中残留的敏感文件。在组策略中启用登录时清空临时文件夹功能可作为纵深防御措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0458","http://www.osvdb.org/915"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0696.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0628","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0628.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0391","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/98 SMB 认证重放漏洞","description":"Windows 95 和 Windows 98 的 SMB 认证机制存在加密挑战值可被重用的安全漏洞。远程攻击者通过捕获并重放合法的 SMB 认证响应数据包，可在未持有用户密码的情况下冒充合法用户身份访问共享资源。该漏洞源于 SMB 协议在认证过程中未对挑战值（challenge）实施一次性使用机制，导致同一挑战值可被多次使用。受影响系统包括 Windows 95、Windows 98、Windows NT、Terminal Server 及 Windows 2000，攻击者需处于同一网络段以嗅探认证流量。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0391"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:17.787","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止支持的 Windows 95/98 系统，Microsoft 未发布官方补丁。建议立即升级至 Windows 10 或 Windows 11 等受支持版本；如无法升级，可在网络边界防火墙禁用 SMB 协议（TCP 139/445 端口）作为临时缓解措施，并限制局域网内不可信设备的接入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91552769809542&w=2","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0391.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6df16fc0c02ccadd2d0fbb0029e3db345d75f1c8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0391.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0391","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ec31d5593e31331ed2058e001803e087d65aa416/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0391.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0391.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9xx2-9vgq-cg78/GHSA-9xx2-9vgq-cg78.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--8bd1c345-0c25-41c6-b5b4-133fdc5ef13a.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0391.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0628.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0719","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0719.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0464","title":"Tripwire Tripwire 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Tripwire 1.2 及更早版本在处理文件系统扫描时未能正确校验文件名长度，本地攻击者可通过创建包含超长文件名的恶意文件触发缓冲区相关问题，导致 Tripwire 程序崩溃或进入异常状态，从而无法完成完整性检测任务。该漏洞需要攻击者具有本地系统访问权限，利用门槛较低，但影响范围仅限于 Tripwire 1.2 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0464"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:27.057","remediation":"建议将 Tripwire 1.2 源码中 src/utils.c 第 387 和 408 行的指针声明从 `char *` 改为 `unsigned char *`，并将 `octal_array` 从 127 个元素扩展到 255 个元素（补丁来自 Bugtraq 公告），重新编译后部署。如无法打补丁，可升级到 Red Hat 提供的已修复版本或使用 AIDE 等现代替代工具。临时缓解措施为限制普通用户在 Tripwire 监控目录中创建超长文件名。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91553066310826&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91592136122066&w=2","http://www.osvdb.org/6609"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0719.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0626","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0626.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0390","title":"SUSE Linux 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"tags.<value>CVE-1999-0390 是 Dosemu（DOS 模拟器）所依赖的 Slang 终端处理库中的缓冲区溢出漏洞。拥有本地系统访问权限的攻击者可向 Dosemu 提交恶意的构造输入，触发 Slang 库在处理数据时发生缓冲区溢出，造成内存损坏。由于 Dosemu 以 setuid root 权限运行，成功利用此漏洞的本地攻击者能够获得 root 级特权，从而完全控制受影响系统，实现机密性、完整性和可用性的全面沦陷。该漏洞影响 SuSE Linux、Caldera OpenLinux 等多种 Linux 发行版，CVSS v2.0 评分为 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0390"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-04","updated":"1999-01-04","remediation":"建议将 dosemu 升级至包含 Slang 库缓冲区溢出修复的版本（Caldera OpenLinux 用户应用 CSSA-1999-006.1 补丁）。Red Hat Linux 用户应升级至 dosemu 0.99.10 或更高版本。如无法升级，可移除或禁用 dosemu 的 setuid 位以缓解提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0626.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1219","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1219.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0914","title":"Debian GNU/Linux netstd FTP客户端缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Debian GNU/Linux 的 netstd 软件包中的 FTP 客户端存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当 FTP 客户端接收到超长或特制的服务器响应时，由于缺乏正确的边界检查，可触发缓冲区溢出。攻击者可通过搭建恶意 FTP 服务器并诱导用户连接，导致客户端崩溃或实现以当前用户权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Debian 2.0 及早期版本系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0914"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-03","updated":"2024-11-20","remediation":"升级 netstd 软件包至包含补丁的最新版本，或使用更安全的替代方案如 openssh sftp/scp。避免使用 FTP 客户端连接不可信的 FTP 服务器，限制 netstd 软件包的使用范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:31:07.393166192+00:00","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/324","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0914"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1219.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0624","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0624.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0389","title":"Debian Linux 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Debian Linux netstd 软件包中的 bootp 服务器存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞触发缓冲区越界写入，导致系统崩溃或执行任意代码。受影响系统为运行 netstd 软件包的 Debian Linux 发行版，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限。成功利用后可获取目标系统的完全控制权，造成机密性、完整性和可用性全面受损。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0389"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-03","updated":"1999-01-03","remediation":"立即升级 netstd 软件包至修复版本：Debian 2.0 (Hamm) 升级至 netstd 2.16-3 或更高版本，Debian 2.1 (Slink) 升级至 netstd 3.07-7.1.slink.1 或更高版本。如未使用 BOOTP 服务，建议禁用 bootpd 守护进程（注释 /etc/inetd.conf 中 bootps 行并重启 inetd），同时考虑迁移至 DHCP 替代已过时的 BOOTP 协议。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0624.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1374","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1374.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1170","title":"Ipswitch IMail 权限提升漏洞","description":"Ipswitch IMail 5.0 及 WS_FTP Server 1.0.1/1.0.2 存在权限提升漏洞。本地攻击者可通过将注册表中 \"flags\" 键值设置为 1920，从而获取额外系统权限，进而修改或添加邮件账户。此漏洞需要攻击者拥有本地访问权限，利用门槛较低，可导致未授权账户操作及系统配置篡改，影响邮件服务及 FTP 服务的正常安全运行。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1170"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:52.153","remediation":"升级 Ipswitch IMail 至 6.0 及以上版本，WS_FTP Server 升级至 2.0 及以上版本。同时使用 regedit 限制注册表项 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\...\\flags 的写入权限，仅允许 Administrators 组修改，并移除普通用户的写权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91816507920544&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/218","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1170.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1170","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1170.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1170.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-ppp7-2732-7vj2/GHSA-ppp7-2732-7vj2.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1170.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/218/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000483.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d6888d56-c1b0-4ee0-94e9-80ee70282bd4.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1374.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0642","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0642.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0402","title":"GNU Wget 符号链接权限修改漏洞","description":"wget 1.5.3 在处理文件权限修改时存在符号链接跟随漏洞。当 wget 使用 chmod 修改下载文件的权限时，如果目标路径是一个符号链接，wget 会错误地跟随该链接并修改链接指向的实际文件的权限，而非符号链接本身的权限。攻击者可以在目标目录中预先创建指向敏感文件（如 /etc/passwd）的符号链接，诱使 wget 修改这些文件的权限，导致本地权限提升或敏感文件被非授权访问。该漏洞影响所有使用 wget 1.5.3 的用户，攻击条件为攻击者需在目标目录有写权限以创建符号链接。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0402"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-02","updated":"2024-06-16","remediation":"升级到 wget 1.6 及以上版本，该版本已修复符号链接跟随问题。对于无法升级的系统，应避免在不可信目录中使用 wget 下载文件，或在使用前手动检查目标路径是否存在符号链接。作为临时缓解措施，可在下载前清理目标目录中的未知符号链接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0402","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0402"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0642.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0991","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0991.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0665","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表不当配置安全漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 中存在一个与系统关键注册表项相关的安全漏洞：某个对系统安全至关重要的注册表键值被设置为不恰当的数值。攻击者若能够访问或修改该注册表项（通常需要本地或远程获得相应权限，或通过其他漏洞达成注册表写入），即可使系统关键安全配置失效，进而破坏系统完整性、提升权限或绕过安全控制。该漏洞影响运行 Microsoft Windows NT 操作系统的相关版本，CVSS 基础评分达 10.0（满分），危害等级为严重，可能导致系统被完全控制。建议尽快检查并修正相关注册表键值，将不当配置恢复为厂商推荐的安全默认值。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0665"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.253","remediation":"立即升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本操作系统，Windows NT 4.0 已于 2004 年停止支持。如无法升级，在注册表编辑器中检查 HKLM\\Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Run 等关键键值的 ACL 权限，移除 Everyone 组的写入权限，并启用 Windows NT 的 ACL 审核策略监控注册表变更。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0665","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0665.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8d0ba8eaeba3ff3558e6044a19d5b454dcc12f33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0665.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0665","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e54d5f68d5b83411d51ab3df8f5c1b120360f139/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0665.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0665.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3c5965e4a3ad0d0b437f880f71224c9e3d8d5fd5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xcr6-jvwv-gjvg/GHSA-xcr6-jvwv-gjvg.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0665.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86265/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0991.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0990","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0990.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0664","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10758,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10778}}","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 系统注册表中存在一处与应用程序运行密切相关的关键注册表项（registry key），其访问控制权限配置不当，赋予了普通用户或低权限进程本不应拥有的修改或写入权限。攻击者在已获得本地普通用户身份的前提下，可通过修改该注册表项的内容，影响依赖该键值运行的高权限应用程序或服务的行为，从而实现本地权限提升，将自身权限提升至系统管理员（SYSTEM）级别。该漏洞影响运行 Windows NT 操作系统的主机，利用条件为攻击者需先获取目标系统的本地登录或普通用户访问权限，无需远程网络访问即可完成利用，CVSS 基础评分为 10.0，危害等级为严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0664"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.140","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 官方针对该漏洞发布的安全补丁（Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 及以上版本）。如无法立即更新，可手动使用 regedt32 将 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services 等关键注册表项的安全权限重置为仅 Administrators 完全控制、普通用户只读，并移除 Everyone 组的写权限，以缓解本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0664","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0664.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8d0ba8eaeba3ff3558e6044a19d5b454dcc12f33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0664.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0664","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e54d5f68d5b83411d51ab3df8f5c1b120360f139/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0664.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0664.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3c5965e4a3ad0d0b437f880f71224c9e3d8d5fd5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-667p-8xxq-6jhg/GHSA-667p-8xxq-6jhg.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0664.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86269/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0990.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0987","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0987.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0663","title":"通用 软件包 系统关键文件完整性校验绕过提权漏洞","description":"系统关键程序、库文件或系统文件的校验和或其他完整性检测指标被篡改，表明这些文件已被恶意修改。攻击者可通过替换或修改系统关键组件，在目标系统上实现权限提升，获取高于预期权限的访问能力。该漏洞影响多种操作系统及软件包管理机制，CVSS评分10.0，危害等级严重。修复方式包括重新安装受影响的软件包并验证文件完整性。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0663"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.027","remediation":"建议立即验证系统关键程序、库文件的完整性校验和，对比官方发布版本的哈希值，发现篡改立即从可信源重新安装受影响组件；启用文件完整性监控（如AIDE/Tripwire）实时监控关键文件变更；启用文件系统完整性保护（如Linux IMA/EVM、Windows系统文件保护）；限制非特权用户对关键系统目录的写入权限，实施最小权限原则；定期对比官方发布的校验和验证系统完整性。如无法立即修复，建议部署运行时应用自我保护（RASP）或主机入侵检测系统（HIDS）监控关键文件完整性变更作为临时缓解措施。建议升级至厂商发布的修复版本或应用官方安全补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0663","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0663.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6719fd7854f40dff0ff13642969f1c4a3c1e227a/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0663.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0663","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e54d5f68d5b83411d51ab3df8f5c1b120360f139/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0663.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0663.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3c5965e4a3ad0d0b437f880f71224c9e3d8d5fd5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c4pr-99gf-f9wv/GHSA-c4pr-99gf-f9wv.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0663.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86268/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0987.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0986","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0986.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0662","title":"Windows 系统关键程序或库未安装安全补丁或服务包","description":"该漏洞并非具体的代码缺陷，而是指运行于 Windows 系统的关键程序、共享库或服务未安装相应的安全补丁、热修复（hotfix）或服务包（service pack），或所使用版本过旧。攻击者可通过探测目标主机已安装的补丁与服务包级别，识别尚未修复的组件，进而利用这些组件中已知的公开漏洞获取系统权限或执行任意代码。其攻击条件为攻击者能够访问目标系统并具备补丁状态探测能力，通常借助网络扫描或服务包注册表检测实现。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0662"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","remediation":"应立即通过 Windows Update 或 WSUS 将系统及所有关键程序、共享库安装至厂商发布的最新安全补丁与服务包级别；对无法自动更新的第三方组件，须手动下载并安装官方发布的最新版本与安全更新；同时启用自动更新策略，定期审计主机已安装的补丁状态，关闭不必要的服务与端口以缩小攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0662","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6719fd7854f40dff0ff13642969f1c4a3c1e227a/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0662.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0662.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e54d5f68d5b83411d51ab3df8f5c1b120360f139/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0662.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0986.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0984","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0984.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0661","title":"Sendmail/TCP Wrappers/OpenSSH 等多款开源软件分发点木马后门漏洞","description":"Sendmail 8.12.6 等多个开源软件的分发服务器遭入侵，攻击者将木马版本替换了原始软件包，用户在下载安装后即被植入后门。受影响的软件包括 TCP Wrappers 7.6、util-linux 2.9g、wu-ftpd 2.2/2.1f、ircII 2.2.9、OpenSSH 3.4p1 及 Sendmail 8.12.6。该漏洞属于供应链投毒攻击，攻击者可在软件分发环节植入恶意代码，导致用户系统被完全控制，危害极大。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0661"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:47.763","remediation":"立即升级 Sendmail 至 8.12.7 或更高版本（如 8.15.2 等长期支持版本），并从官方站点 sendmail.org 重新下载验证过签名的源码包；无法立即升级时，请从可信镜像站重新获取源码并校验 PGP 签名（PGP 密钥 ID：0x7B7C7C7C），同时在防火墙层面限制 25 端口仅对可信中继开放，禁止直接暴露在公网。升级后务必重新编译安装并重启 sendmail 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=102820843403741&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=102821663814127&w=2","http://online.securityfocus.com/archive/1/294539","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1994-07.html","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1994-14.html","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1999-01.html","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1999-02.html","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-2002-28.html","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/10313.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/5921","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/21919","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0661.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6719fd7854f40dff0ff13642969f1c4a3c1e227a/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0661.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0661","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0661.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3c5965e4a3ad0d0b437f880f71224c9e3d8d5fd5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8wmh-7mx7-jf2g/GHSA-8wmh-7mx7-jf2g.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0661.json","https://github.com/tstromberg/supplychain-attack-data/blob/3300044eadff42ffbaf5e6cd038faad520519779/_site/attack/sendmail/index.html","https://github.com/phx/cvescan/blob/d8d463e490d1d2d785179e8ace7ff59c2ea15f1f/README.md","https://github.com/privy-cafe/DollarLinuxClub/blob/57ae5d72b23dd6fe9fc5fca4dd120ffdf9dca123/misc/efnetretards.txt","https://github.com/Orlando-pt/Proj1_SIO/blob/8662cbb45832bd6f158c073e145d84def5bd04a9/tratado/cve/cve%2B6.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0984.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0983","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0983.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0660","title":"通用 后门/特洛伊木马 系统植入漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0660 已被 CVE 官方拒绝使用。该候选编号原用于描述一类系统被植入黑客工具、后门程序或木马（例如 NetBus、Back Orifice、Rootkit 等）的安全场景，而非指向某个特定产品、协议或设计缺陷。此类配置安全问题更适合纳入通用配置枚举（CCE）覆盖范围。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0660"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.443","remediation":"部署应用白名单策略（如 Windows AppLocker 或 SRP），仅允许经授权的软件运行；部署终端检测与响应（EDR）系统实时监控进程创建和网络连接异常；启用防病毒软件并保持病毒库每日更新；实施最小权限原则，限制用户安装软件的权限；定期进行全盘安全扫描和完整性校验。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0983.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0982","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0982.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0659","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 域控制器配置检测","description":"CVE-1999-0659 已被拒绝（REJECT），该条目原用于标识 Windows NT 主域控制器或备份域控制器的存在状态，这属于系统配置枚举范畴而非实际安全漏洞。NVD 官方说明指出此类配置信息更适合通过公共配置枚举标准覆盖，因此废弃该编号。该条目没有实际的安全风险、攻击条件或利用方式，CVSS 评分为 0。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0659"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:00.407","remediation":"确保域控制器仅部署在受控内部网络段，禁用不必要的 NetBIOS/SMB 广播发现；对 Windows NT 4.0 系统，建议升级至 Active Directory 架构（Windows 2000+）并部署最新安全更新；通过防火墙限制 135/TCP、139/TCP、445/TCP、389/TCP 端口仅向授权管理段开放；定期审计域控制器暴露面，禁用 LM/NTLMv1 认证协议。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0982.toml"}]